                    ],
                    "stepSolveAnswerUnits": "km/s/Mpc",
                    "stepConcepts": [
                        "c413a452-cd00-445d-b07a-3c69cb5d60aa",
                        "ae5906b8-745a-436d-8695-00ba2c22369f"
                    ],
                    "options": []
                },
                {
                    "id": "c30d0da674a243f9a1ceb",
                    "stepText": "Now that we have calculated the Hubble Constant, let's identify the formula that relates it to the estimated age of the Universe. Which of the following formulas shows that the age of the Universe is inversely proportional to the Hubble Constant?",
